HEADWORD: Dendrolite
<hw>Den"dro*lite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>de`ndron</grk> tree + <ets>-lite</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>dendrolithe</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Paleon.)</fld> <def>A petrified or
fossil shrub, plant, or part of a plant.</def>⟦br⟧
